reviewText: Good story.  Very entertaining.  If you like gay stories this is one of the rare good ones.

The DVD cover says this is about 4 people in Madrid looking to ease their loneliness. My thoughts...it is a whole bunch of people making a confused and bad movie. I can honestly say I felt absolutely nothing for any of them. I love foreign films but this one..please take it out back and put it out of its misery. truthfully I should have gone one star but the guy on the cover is pretty cute.
Thankfully it was only 70 minutes long so I endured it.  Senseless, no purpose to any of it.  Just a bunch of people living miserable lives. There was so much smoking of cigarettes, it was crazy.
